title: 2020 CFB Pick Em Week 6
description:
El Pres, Big Cat & Rico Bosco are back for another week of picks. Rico is via zoom again and the Ryders are in need this week. Big Cat remains in the lead for the Pat Hill Trophy but Dave has another huge card in a close second!


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
